text: Jogeshwari East Vidhan Sabha constituency is one of the 26 Vidhan Sabha constituencies located in the Mumbai Suburban district. Jogeshwari East is part of the Mumbai North West Lok Sabha constituency along with five other Vidhan Sabha segments, namely Goregaon, Versova, Dindoshi, Andheri West and Andheri West in the Mumbai Suburban district. ==Members of Legislative Assembly== Key {| class="wikitable" |- ! colspan="2"|Election !
